   "source": [
    "picks = mne.pick_types(raw.info, meg=False, fnirs=True)\n",
    "dists = mne.preprocessing.nirs.source_detector_distances(raw.info, picks=picks)\n",
    "raw.pick(picks[dists > 0.01])\n",
    "raw.plot(n_channels=len(raw.ch_names), duration=500, show_scrollbars=False)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
